					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2216193#post-3759269</guid>
				<title>Last slots used in each section as Series IV filled up</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2216193/scp-series-4#post-3759269</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 04 Apr 2018 18:11:47 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ObserverSeptember</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1488791</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Figured I'd post this here for anyone who is interested. Will update this list as each section is filled up.</p> <p>NOTE: This list does not include slots that were later deleted and refilled by another article; this only reflects when each section first became full.</p> <p><strong>3000s</strong>: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3061">SCP-3061</a> - Reluctant Fiend (<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/penton" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1998745&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537107347" alt="Penton" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1998745)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/penton" >Penton</a></span>, 24 Jan 2018)</p> <p><strong>3100s</strong>: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3189">SCP-3189</a> - For The Man Who Has Everything (<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537107347" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" >DrChandra</a></span>, 3 Apr 2018)</p> <p><strong>3300s</strong>: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3352">SCP-3352</a> - My Better Half (<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/humidhermit" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3956486&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537107347" alt="HumidHermit" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3956486)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/humidhermit" >HumidHermit</a></span>, 6 Aug 2018)</p> <p><strong>3200s:</strong> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3284">SCP-3284</a> - Uncontainable (<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jim-north" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2191727&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537107347" alt="Jim North" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2191727)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jim-north" >Jim North</a></span>, 12 Aug 2018)</p> <p><strong>3900s:</strong> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3953">SCP-3953</a> - Costa Rica…<strong>IN SPACE</strong> (<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dramps" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4209325&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537107347" alt="Dramps" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4209325)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dramps" >Dramps</a></span>, 1 Sep 2018]])</p> 
